		<Folder>
			<name>🐘 Elephant Trajectories (BCRW + OSM)</name>
			<description>Synthetic Asian elephant trajectories — Walayar Range Forest.
BCRW model: Step~Gamma(α=0.90), Heading~WrappedCauchy(ρ).
Refs: Varma et al. 2012; Benhamou 2006; Codling et al. 2008.</description>
			<Folder>
				<name>Forest Forager</name>
				<description>Cow/calf group foraging in deep forest interior. High directional persistence during travel; strong forest interior preference; moderate water attraction; strong daytime settlement avoidance. Most common movement pattern in Walayar (Varma et al. 2012). Ref: Sukumar 2003; Gubbi 2012 β_forest=+0.40.</description>
