			<Folder>
				<name>Agricultural Raider</name>
				<description>Retreats to deep forest interior during daylight; approaches forest–agriculture boundary at dusk for crop-raiding. Walayar peak raid season: October–March (Varma et al. 2012). 93% of raids occur between 18:30 and 06:00 (Sitati et al. 2005). Refs: Sukumar &amp; Gadgil 1988; Baskaran et al. 2010; Varma et al. 2012.</description>
