				<description>Adult bull with wide-ranging movement; crosses between forest sections and uses the Palakkad corridor. Low directional persistence → large-area coverage. Refs: Baskaran et al. 1995 (85–350 km² home range); Varma et al. 2012 (max 312 km² in Walayar); Douglas-Hamilton et al. 2005 (bull dispersal corridors).</description>
