			<Folder>
				<name>Riparian Corridor</name>
				<description>Dry-season concentration in riparian corridors (Walayar River and stream network). Very high water attraction following the river gradient. Home range contracts to river corridor in dry season. Refs: de Silva et al. 2011 (Sri Lanka dry-season riparian contraction); Wittemyer et al. 2008 (river corridor use); Varma et al. 2012 (Walayar river as water source).</description>
